Flow of JEE application

browser -> web server -> servlet -> view ( JSP / Freemarket )

MVC flow
To work with JSP variables, it has to be put into model
Model			  - 										ToDo.java
View 			  - Show whatever it is in the model 		login.jsp
Controler/Servlet - directs to view, control the flow		LoginController.java

Modeified MVC flow

Front controller - dispatcherServlet picks
				 - > LoginController, ToDoController
		
Spring Boot
Easy to build to production grade